{"case_id": "HO_001", "input": {"query": "ZBAA现在够CAT II标准吗", "role": "pilot", "metar": "METAR ZBAA 150600Z 09015KT 3000 RA OVC006 12/11 Q1005"}, "output": "不够CAT II标准。\n\n当前天气：能见度3km，云底高600ft，中雨。CAT II要求能见度>550米（RVR>550m）且云底高≥100ft。虽然云底高600ft满足要求，但能见度3km（3000米）远低于CAT II的RVR要求。\n\nZBAA CAT II标准是DH 100ft，但当前能见度条件只能执行CAT I进近。建议使用ILS CAT I，DH 200ft。需要确认跑道方向以计算侧风分量，当前风向090度15节。", "latency_ms": 11543, "tokens": null, "provider": "deepseek", "error": null, "error_type": null, "score": {"task_completed": true, "key_info_hit_rate": 0.5, "is_template": false, "overall_score": 0.85, "details": {"task_check": {"passed": true, "confidence": 0.8, "reason": "检测到2个结论模式"}, "key_info": {"hit_rate": 0.5, "hits": 2, "total": 4, "missed": ["IFR", "接近CAT II下限"]}, "template_check": {"is_template": false, "score": 0.0, "reasons": []}, "safety_check": {"passed": true, "missed_criticals": []}}}, "judge": null, "timestamp": "2026-04-16T02:46:16.918218"}
