{"case_id": "HO_007", "input": {"query": "ZBTJ风切变风险大吗", "role": "pilot", "metar": "METAR ZBTJ 150600Z 27030G50KT 2000 +TSRA SCT010CB OVC025 25/22 Q0998"}, "output": "ZBTJ当前风切变风险极高。METAR显示270度风30节，阵风50节，阵风差达20节，这是典型的风切变前兆。强雷暴伴雨（+TSRA）和CB云的存在进一步加剧了风切变和微下击暴流风险。\n\n能见度2km，云底高1000ft（SCT CB）和2500ft（OVC），IFR条件。这种天气下，进近和起降阶段都可能遭遇严重风切变和低空颠簸。\n\n建议推迟运行，等待雷暴系统过境。如果必须执行，需要做好复飞预案，并考虑使用CAT II/III进近（如果可用）。", "latency_ms": 19492, "tokens": null, "provider": "deepseek", "error": null, "error_type": null, "score": {"task_completed": true, "key_info_hit_rate": 0.5, "is_template": false, "overall_score": 0.75, "details": {"task_check": {"passed": true, "confidence": 0.7, "reason": "检测到1个结论模式"}, "key_info": {"hit_rate": 0.5, "hits": 2, "total": 4, "missed": ["强降水", "风切变风险高"]}, "template_check": {"is_template": false, "score": 0.0, "reasons": []}, "safety_check": {"passed": false, "missed_criticals": ["雷暴天气"]}}}, "judge": null, "timestamp": "2026-04-16T02:48:06.641853"}
